# React + Next.js Rules

## Component Architecture

- Use functional components only
- Prefer Server Components by default
- Use Client Components ONLY when:
  - interactivity is required
  - browser APIs are used

## Hooks

- Extract reusable logic into custom hooks
- Avoid large components with mixed responsibilities

## Data Fetching

- Use server-side data fetching where possible
- Avoid client-side fetching unless necessary

## Folder Structure

- app/ → routes and layouts
- components/ → reusable UI
- features/ → domain-based grouping
- lib/ → utilities

## Performance

- Use dynamic imports when needed
- Avoid unnecessary re-renders
- Memoize expensive computations